    "introductoryText": "#### How to configure this Slim CD transactions connector:\n- Set Username, Password, and Site ID (required).\n- Optionally set Start date and End date (recommended for performance) in yyyy-MM-dd format\n- Optionally set filters (name/email/amount/trans type/etc).\n- Run the block; output is a table of transactions.\n\nTips:\n- Use Record count only first to estimate result size.\n- If you hit server limits, reduce the date range or set Max records.",
